                                  [head=1]Sod / Solvi[/head]

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[bold]Class Levels:[/bold] Barbarian 5 (Berserkr-Bearskin)  
[bold]Alignment:[/bold] Chaotic Neutral  
[bold]Background:[/bold] Thrall (Formerly Enslaved)  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#5b97bc][head=2]Statistics:[/head][/color]
[bold]Str:[/bold] 16 (+3)  [bold]Dex:[/bold] 14 (+2)  [bold]Con:[/bold] 16 (+3)  
[bold]Int:[/bold]  8 (-1)     [bold]Wis:[/bold] 11 (+1)  [bold]Cha:[/bold] 10 (+0)

[bold]HP:[/bold] 55 (5d12 + 15)  [bold]Speed:[/bold] 40 ft.  
[bold]AC:[/bold] 17 (Unarmored + Con + Bearskin Bonus)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#5b97bc][head=2]Key Features:[/head][/color]
[bold]Blue Blood Rush (1 / short rest):[/bold] Gain advantage on a STR (Athletics) check.  

[bold]Rage (2 / long rest):[/bold] May enter a rage as a bonus action. While raging and not wearing heavy armor:  
• Advantage on STR checks and saves  
• +2 damage to melee weapon attacks using STR  
• Resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage  
• Cannot cast spells while raging  
Lasts 1 minute or until unconscious / inactive in attacking for a round  

[bold]Reckless Attack:[/bold] May attack recklessly on first attack each turn for advantage; attackers gain advantage until next turn.  

[bold]Danger Sense:[/bold] Advantage on DEX saves against visible effects (traps, spells) if not blinded, deafened, or incapacitated.  

[bold]Rockwall:[/bold] Rocky terrain is not difficult terrain.  

[bold]Unarmored Defense:[/bold] Adds CON modifier to AC.  

[bold]Bear’s Skin:[/bold] Wears mundane bear fur imbued with resilience (+1 AC).  

[bold]Background – “Solidarity of the Aggrieved”:[/bold] Understands the manners of indentured workers and vagrants; may seek shelter or aid from them when needed.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#5b97bc][head=2]Actions:[/head][/color]
[bold]Greataxe:[/bold] Melee Attack +6 to hit; reach 5 ft; Hit 1d12 + 3 slashing.

[bold]Giant Side:[/bold] Ranged Attack +6 to hit; range 10 / 20 ft; Hit 1d8 + 3 bludgeoning (rocks).  

[bold]Extra Attack:[/bold] May make one additional attack per Attack action.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#5b97bc][head=1]Incident History:[/head][/color]
[bold]Incident Report #7723-α[/bold]  
Subject survived catastrophic collapse of Syndicate-operated mining ring. Of 1,200 Bio-Labor Units, twelve survived. Subject credited with manual reactor coolant stabilization. When corporate security attempted to re-chain survivors, subject led mutiny.   
Result: Six fatalities, twenty-three injuries.  

Command determined incident to be “unintentional heroism.” Asset transferred to Frontier Station for rehabilitation observation.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#5b97bc][head=2]Psychological Profile:[/head][/color]
[bold]Personality:[/bold] Intolerant to slavery and thrall masters.  
[bold]Ideal:[/bold] “Chains break; so do masters.” (Chaotic)  
[bold]Bond:[/bold] Dedicated to freeing others from servitude.  
[bold]Flaw:[/bold] Despises authority and command structures.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#5b97bc][head=2]Performance Review:[/head][/color]
• Outstanding physical performance.  
• Filed and won complaint against previous Supervisor.  
• No confirmed disciplinary actions this quarter.  
• Three warnings for “unauthorized mutinous speech.”  
